The State Fair of West Virginia is annually held in mid-August on the State Fairgrounds in Lewisburg, West Virginia. The 2022 State Fair of West Virginia is scheduled for August 11-20, 2022. The State Fairgrounds consists of a large open Midway for a carnival, grandstands for live performances, and several exhibition buildings. Free parking is provided adjacent to the fairgrounds.

This app is designed to be an all-encompassing guide for the 2022 State Fair of West Virginia. Features within the app include attractions, schedules, maps, and food information.
